column.name: recipe
column.value: Cut the meat, onions and put in a pan with hot butter. Fry and then put the eggs in the bowl. Mix a moment. Enjoy your meal!

column.name: recipe
column.value: Slice the bread. Brush with butter. Put cold cuts and cheese. Decorate with ketchup.

column.name: recipe
column.value: Mix everything together, add delicacies at the end, mix. Pour onto a baking tray and bake for about 1 hour at 200 degrees. After baking and cooling the cake, make a topping. Dissolve all ingredients in a saucepan, do not boil. Pour the dough over the hot topping. You can sprinkle with coconut for the effect.
